OL,6, soaring energy bills have hit a crisis 
OL,7, point, with more help needed.          
OL,9,F"It will be desperate," the consumer   
OL,10,Fchampion said. "It's going to throw    
OL,11,Fmany households into a terribly        
OL,12,Fdifficult financial situation."        
